item.title: First sig in a long time
item.dc:creator: @exe626 exe626
item.description:
@exe626 wrote:

[quote=“nator123123, post:8, topic:152021”]MY EYES, THEY BURN!!!

Did you happen to use gausian blur?
Looking at Itachi, which is the FOCAL, HURTS MY EYES. When you blur it, erase the blur on the focal.

I guess that’s pretty good for a long time…[/quote]…Chill out please? Lets try to be a little bit mature.

  1. The render is blurred badly. You shouldn’t blur what you want people to focus on.
  2. The lensflare in the upper left is throwing me off; you should have considered blurring it and smudging it.
  3. The text seems to be the focal point in this. You don’t want people to spend their entire time paying attention to the text, you want that to be a ‘brand’, so people can’t steal it.
    4)I don’t really understand the background, but at least your colors work.

Read full topic
